  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech系统画一个完整的HIPAA合规数据流图。核心是从HIPAA Vault出发，经过LabAnalyzer做分析。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LabAnalyzer是一个判断节点对吧？那它的两个分支怎么命名，成功和失败？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，成功就回到Vault做存储，失败的话要同步到EMR系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把B节点做成菱形判断，两条分支分别标Success和Failure，Z节点用红色背景突出失败路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "成功存储后，数据要流向PatientRecords，然后再回到LabAnalyzer做一次复核。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "C到D，D再到E，这个闭环我记下了。E节点我做成绿色背景，表示这是进入策略评估区的入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这里需要加一个子图，叫Policy Evaluation，专门处理诊断引擎的准入逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Policy Evaluation",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "子图内部怎么流转？从E节点进去之后第一步是什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Policy Evaluation",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "E先到F，F是另一个HIPAA Vault检查点，判断数据权限是否匹配。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
