      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "风格上需要区分一下：Vault用粉色，判断节点用灰色，失败路径用红色，Policy Evaluation里的节点统一绿色，最后的引擎用蓝色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
